Cell["\<\
This Demonstration shows the importance of making extra payments on a typical \
amortizing loan, such as a principal and interest mortgage. Even small \
amounts over and above the prescribed minimum can substantially reduce the \
term of the loan and the overall amount of interest paid.\
\>", "Text"]
}, Close]]
